      <p>Buying new equipment is exciting — until you see the price tag. A new excavator costs RM400,000+. A forklift? RM80,000-RM150,000. For most Malaysian SMEs, paying cash upfront isn't realistic (and even if you can, it's not always smart).</p>
      
