        <h3>For Companies (Sdn Bhd / Enterprise)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Business age:</strong> At least 2 years of operations (some lenders accept 1 year)</li>
          <li><strong>Revenue:</strong> Minimum RM500,000 per year (varies by equipment cost)</li>
          <li><strong>Documents:</strong> SSM, financial statements (2 years), bank statements (6 months), purchase quotation</li>
          <li><strong>Director's commitment:</strong> Personal guarantee from majority shareholder</li>
          <li><strong>Down payment:</strong> Typically 10-20% of equipment cost</li>
        </ul>
        
