        <ul>
          <li><strong>Business age:</strong> At least 3 years</li>
          <li><strong>Revenue:</strong> Consistent income shown in bank statements</li>
          <li><strong>Documents:</strong> Business registration, income tax returns, bank statements (6-12 months), purchase quotation</li>
          <li><strong>Credit history:</strong> Clean or manageable CCRIS/CTOS</li>
          <li><strong>Down payment:</strong> 20-30% typical</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Don't have perfect credit?</strong> We work with many lenders — some are more flexible if you have a strong business track record, loyal customers, or existing contracts. Let's find a solution that works for you.</p>

      <h2>The New Equipment Financing Process (Step-by-Step)</h2>
      
